The '''Harem Cave''' was a cave, usually, where [[Killik/Legends|Killiks]] would go to mate after participating in the [[Dawn Rumble]]. [[Joiner]]s who had participated in the dance would often go there as well, presumably for the same purpose, though whether or not they mingled with the insects or occupied different areas is unknown.

